        public Resource createdResource(String key)
        Gets a resource created by a creatable task in this group.

        This method can return null if the resource has not yet created that happens if the responsible task is not yet selected for execution or it's it progress

      • executeRootTask

        public void executeRootTask(TaskItem<Resource> task)
                     throws Exception
        Description copied from class: TaskGroupBase
        Executes the root task in this group.

        This method will be invoked when all the task dependencies of the root task are finished executing, at this point root task can be executed by consuming the result of tasks it depends on.
